General definitions
.sp 3mm
Private card - private liability
:SKRSLUT.
.br
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You are solely and personally responsible for all
payments, withdrawals and other debits made using the
card. Your liability also covers losses attributable to
unauthorised use of the card by others, 
although with the
limitations pursuant to Section 62 of the Danish Act on
Payment Services. See Article 2.9.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Family card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A MasterCard issued in connection with a Private card. No separate card
account is set up for a Family card, as all use of the card is
attributed to the card account established in connection with the
Private card which is a precondition for the issuing of a Family card.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Corporate card - corporate liability
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A MasterCard Business used to cover expenses that the cardholder
pays on behalf of his/her place of employment/company.
