Card types
.sp 3mm
Private card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
MasterCard cards are issued to private individuals for private use.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Family card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
An extra, private MasterCard that the holder of a Private card has
issued to his/her spouse/life partner or to one of his/her children who
is aged over 18 and still living at home.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
Corporate card
:SKRSLUT.
.br
MasterCard Business cards are issued to private individuals for corporate
purchases.
